ES5 Global Constants

var PI = 3.14;
PI = 42; // stop me from doing this!

I can't stop you from doing this with ES5.

ES2015 Global Constants

/* Write an ES2015 Version */
const PI = 3.14;
PI = 42; // Error!

Quiz

What is the difference between var and let?
var allows variable redeclaration whereas let doesn't. var allows access to hoisted variable wheras let 
doesn't. var creates function scope whereas let creates block scope.

What is the difference between var and const?
var allows variable redeclarartion and reassignment whereas const doesn't allow either. var allows access
to hoisted variable wheras const doesn't. var creates function scope whereas const creates block scope.

What is the difference between let and const?
let allows variable reassignment whereas const doesn't.

What is hoisting?
In JS a variable declared with var is known by the compiler before its actual declaration both globally
and within a function.
